  <p class="bio">
    I am a first-year doctoral researcher at Aalto University, supervised by Prof. Yu Xiao. My research focuses on cross-modal retrieval and representation, with applications in visual document retrieval, human motion understanding, and e-textile sensing. Previously, I obtained a dual M.Sc. in Data Science from KTH and Aalto (EIT Digital, GPA 4.56/5.0), and interned at ABB Corporate Research working on knowledge graph-enhanced RAG systems. I am also a Kaggle Competitions Master (top 0.5% globally).
